In Kundalini yoga that discipline is a 40-day sadhana practice of yoga and #meditation.

This #workshop will #inspire you to begin a 40 day practice or renew your sadhana by delving deep into the answers to these 4 questions:  Why do I need this #discipline ?  How can I achieve my #goals ?  When is the best #time for me to #practice ? Where is the best location for my #sadhana
